(FR) Mr President, I should like to invoke the Rules of Procedure.
I feel obliged to point out - as I said a moment ago - that the report by Mr PomÃ©s Ruiz is not available in French, or, to be more precise, the version of this report presented as the French version contains the biography of the candidate as well as a reply to questions exclusively in English, which seems to me to violate our Rules of Procedure.
